# Copy values into Railway → Project → Variables (same names).
# After deploy, use: https://<your-service>.up.railway.app/api/corpse-log
# In the executor hub set: _G.FENTI_CORPSE_LOG_RELAY_URL and _G.FENTI_CORPSE_LOG_RELAY_KEY (Bearer secret).
